'''圣安德肋堂'''（Chiesa di Sant'Andrea）是一座罗马天主教教堂，位于[[意大利|意大利]][[卡普里岛|卡普里岛]]南部的小港（Marina Piccola）附近，1900年为当地渔民兴建<ref name="BennettKavanagh2011">{{cite book|last1=Bennett|first1=Martin Wilmot|last2=Kavanagh|first2=Fergal|last3=Squillante|first3=Fiorella|title=Fodor's the Amalfi Coast, Capri & Naples|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=3ecCDwhHA_cC&pg=PA115|accessdate=10 July 2012|date=18 October 2011|publisher=Random House Digital, Inc.|isbn=978-0-679-00933-7|pages=115–}}</ref>。该堂所在地点原有一个瞭望塔<ref name="CN">{{cite web|url=http://www.capri.net/en/churches|title=Church of Sant'Andrea|publisher=Capri.net|accessdate=11 July 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120618224456/http://www.capri.net/en/churches|archive-date=2012-06-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。该堂由画家Riccardo Fainardi设计，德国银行家乌戈·安德烈亚斯夫妇资助<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.capritourism.com/en/article?article1_id=1703|title=Chiesa di Sant'Andrea|publisher=Capritourism.com|accessdate=11 July 2012|archive-date=2016-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160924084343/http://www.capritourism.com/en/article?article1_id=1703|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

